  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="SK">Budovanie kapac&#xED;t rozvojov&#xE9;ho oddelenia diec&#xE9;zy Adigrat</narrative>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Capacity Building of the Development Division of the Diocese of Adigrat</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="SK">Dobrovo&#x13E;n&#xED;k sa bude s&#xFA;stre&#x10F;ova&#x165; na pr&#xE1;cu so zamestnancami rozvojov&#xE9;ho oddelenia diec&#xE9;zy. V prvej f&#xE1;ze pobytu zrealizuje zmapovanie ich konkr&#xE9;tnych potrieb v oblasti budovania kapac&#xED;t (komunik&#xE1;cia v anglickom jazyku, pr&#xED;prava narat&#xED;vnych a finan&#x10D;n&#xFD;ch spr&#xE1;v, pr&#xED;prava rozpo&#x10D;tov, monitoring a evalu&#xE1;cia, vyh&#x13E;ad&#xE1;vanie inform&#xE1;ci&#xED; na internete a pod.) a na ich z&#xE1;klade priprav&#xED; individu&#xE1;lny a skupinov&#xFD; harmonogram tr&#xE9;ningov a konzult&#xE1;ci&#xED;.</narrative>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Volunteer will focus on working with staff development department of the diocese. A specific needs assesment will be carried out - in the area of &#x200B;&#x200B;capacity building, communication in English, preparation of narrative and financial reports, budget planning, monitoring and evaluation, information retrieval on the Internet, etc..</narrative>
  </description>
